16
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:47,049
All that I know is that
you have become his target as well.

17
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:49,049
Whose?

18
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:51,079
The little devil.

19
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:57,390
- Who are you?
- He may be young, but he's a devil.

20
00:01:59,260 --> 00:02:01,959
I'm only doing this
to protect my daughter.

21
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:06,400
But then again, my memory
will be erased again soon.

22
