He's here.

25
00:02:29,789 --> 00:02:31,389
Don't underestimate him...

26
00:02:32,490 --> 00:02:34,060
unless you want to die
a gruesome death.

27
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,000
What did you do to Sang Ah?

28
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:47,009
I did everything you told me to do.

29
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,280
I'll kill you.

30
