156
00:14:59,769 --> 00:15:02,610
Dong Baek ran away last night.

157
00:15:02,639 --> 00:15:05,009
I'll end the briefing here.

158
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:07,980
From this moment on,
Dong Baek will be our key suspect.

159
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:09,980
He will be your top priority.

160
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:13,149
We believe Senior Superintendent
Han Sun Mi, Captain Koo Kyung Tan,

161
00:15:13,149 --> 00:15:15,090
and Constable Oh Se Hoon
will be aiding him.

162
00:15:15,090 --> 00:15:17,759
Track and monitor them.

163
00:15:17,789 --> 00:15:19,190
