169
00:15:25,559 --> 00:15:28,129
- Am I right or wrong?
- You're right.

170
00:15:28,399 --> 00:15:29,929
He does seem suspicious.

171
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,039
What did you just say?

172
00:15:33,169 --> 00:15:34,970
