174
00:15:36,539 --> 00:15:38,139
If he refuses to be arrested,

175
00:15:38,610 --> 00:15:40,840
you're allowed to use
any kind of force.

176
00:15:41,409 --> 00:15:42,809
Even guns?

177
00:15:43,809 --> 00:15:46,720
Sir, who gave you these orders?

178
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:49,549
Even those stupid prosecutors
wouldn't give such orders.

179
00:15:49,549 --> 00:15:52,389
Dong Baek is one crazy guy.
He won't give in that easily.

180
00:15:52,389 --> 00:15:53,620
And yet, you want us to use guns?

181
00:15:53,759 --> 00:15:56,629
You know he has a temper.
Are you telling us to kill him?

182
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:59,460
- Am I right or wrong?
- You're right.

183
00:16:03,070 --> 00:16:07,639
(Chief Byun Young Soo)

184
00:16:10,509 --> 00:16:11,940
Show me the proof, sir.

185
00:16:15,879 --> 00:16:19,220
Hey, Young Soo.
Are you refusing to obey me?

186
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:20,980
No, sir.
I only wish to see the proof.

187
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:22,490
The prosecutor didn't request
for your help...

188
00:16:22,490 --> 00:16:23,950
when he got the arrest warrant.

189
00:16:25,690 --> 00:16:27,519
Catch him before the prosecution
does and find proof.

190
00:16:27,519 --> 00:16:29,559
That's your job.
Don't be impudent...

191
00:16:30,129 --> 00:16:32,059
and demand to see proof!

