208
00:17:50,710 --> 00:17:52,039
("Dong Baek Is a Heinous Suspect,
Did He Deceive Everyone?")

209
00:17:52,039 --> 00:17:54,140
Reporter Kang Ji Eun's agency
wrote this.

210
00:17:54,549 --> 00:17:57,009
The press won't side with Baek.

211
00:17:57,480 --> 00:18:00,250
We're the only ones he has,
so stay awake.

212
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,650
