You're alive.

217
00:19:45,890 --> 00:19:47,390
How did you know I was here?

218
00:19:48,329 --> 00:19:49,390
Sit down.

219
00:19:51,829 --> 00:19:53,430
This feels like an interrogation.

220
00:19:54,059 --> 00:19:55,269
That's because it is.

221
00:19:57,470 --> 00:19:58,539
About what?

222
00:19:58,700 --> 00:20:00,140
I want to know the truth about you.

223
00:20:01,710 --> 00:20:04,009
